Okay so I was looking through the help section and noticed that someone had asked for this so I thought if they didn't know how to do it that means no one has posted it yet? So here it is.

Goto src/server/model/players/client.java

and add this code

[code]public void loginMessage() {
            for (int j = 0; j < Server.playerHandler.players.length; j++) {
               if (Server.playerHandler.players[j] != null) {
                  Client c2 = (Client)Server.playerHandler.players[j];
                  switch (playerRights){
                     case 0: //Regular Player
                        c2.sendMessage("[PLAYER] "+playerName+" has logged in.");
                     break;
                     case 1: //Donator
                        c2.sendMessage("[DONATOR] "+playerName+" has logged in.");
                     break;
                     case 2:
                        c2.sendMessage("@gre@[Moderator] "+playerName+" has logged in.");
                     break;
                     case 3:
                        c2.sendMessage("[GLOBAL MODERATOR] "+playerName+" has logged in.");
                     break;
                     case 4:
                        c2.sendMessage("@yel@[Adminstrator "+playerName+" has logged in.");
                     break;
                     case 5:
                        c2.sendMessage("@red@[Owner] "+playerName+" has logged in.");
                     break;
                  }
               }
            }
   }[/code]

If I have missed anything then please let me know because I have just ripped this code out of my server files.
